Response: { "matches": [{ "file": "/var/log/syslog", "line": 2001, "text": "Oct 12 11:00:00 server kernel: [Warning] low memory" }, { "file": "/var/log/dpkg.log", "line": 450, "text": "2023-10-12 10:30:00 WARNING config file missing" }], "count": 2 }

Question: Count occurrences of "root" in /etc recursively.
Call: { "func_call": "grep_count", "pattern": "root", "path": "/etc", "flags": "-r" }
Response: { "matches": [], "count": 27 }

